item.title: It’s time to rethink assessment for learning
item.description: AI is reshaping classrooms and careers, and assessment design must keep pace. For decades, formative assessment has been a silent engine for learning—powering insights about student progress and worker readiness. But let’s be honest, in a world where technology is evolving faster than human skills, it’s time to ask questions about traditional teaching and learning models, and in many cases, modernize them....
